OL,3,CControversial plans to build homes on
OL,4,Chistoric grassland set to be approved
OL,6,FControversial plans to build 260 homes
OL,7,Fon historic grassland in Bristol are
OL,8,Fexpected to be approved later tonight.
OL,10,FFor 15 years, campaigners have battled
OL,11,Fto save Brislington Meadows for its
OL,12,Fvaluable biodiversity and wildlife.
OL,14,FHowever, the developer says more than
OL,15,Fhalf of the area will be kept as green
OL,16,Fspace and Homes England insists the
OL,17,Fhomes are necessary to help alleviate
OL,18,Fthe housing crisis in Bristol.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
