OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1773392677
OL,3,CControversial plans to build homes on
OL,4,Chistoric grassland set to be approved
OL,6,FLucy Bell-Reeves, from the campaign
OL,7,Fgroup Save Brislington Meadows, wants
OL,8,Fto save it from development because
OL,9,Fshe says it's a unique and precious
OL,10,Fsite.
OL,12,F"You don't really have open spaces
OL,13,Flike this anywhere else in Bristol. In
OL,14,Fthe summer this meadow is waist height
OL,15,Fwith all types of different grasses,
OL,16,Fin the winter you get all the
OL,17,Fdifferent berries on the trees when
OL,18,Fyou come in spring you hear the birds
OL,19,Fin the hedgerows.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1773392677
OL,3,CControversial plans to build homes on
OL,4,Chistoric grassland set to be approved
OL,6,F"Bristol is a very busy centre but
OL,7,Fwhen you come up here you can just
OL,8,Fslow down and appreciate nature."
OL,10,FOutline planning permission was
OL,11,Fgranted for the homes in April 2023
OL,12,Fafter the government's planning
OL,13,Finspectorate overruled the council on
OL,14,Fappeal.
OL,16,FMayor Marvin Rees wrote at the time he
OL,17,Fwas "deeply disappointed to see the
OL,18,Fgovernment approve plans to build on
OL,19,FBrislington Meadows ` this wildlife
OL,20,Fhaven needs protection.
OL,26,@pD@aO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1773392677
OL,3,CControversial plans to build homes on
OL,4,Chistoric grassland set to be approved
OL,6,FDetailed plans are due to be voted on
OL,7,Fby councillors tonight. The developer
OL,8,FKeepmoat described the 260 homes as
OL,9,F"high quality new family homes of
OL,10,Fwhich 30% are affordable, alongside
OL,11,Fsignificant green space."
OL,13,FThey add "it will also create a
OL,14,Fthriving new community in a
OL,15,Fsustainable location close to shops,
OL,16,Fcommunity facilities, employment areas
OL,17,Fand local transport infrastructure."
OL,19,FHowever, campaigners want as much
OL,20,Fbiodiversity protected on the meadows
OL,21,Fas possible.
OL,26,@qD@AOUsD@YO]uD@JOUyD@dO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1773392677
OL,3,CControversial plans to build homes on
OL,4,Chistoric grassland set to be approved
OL,6,FLucy said: "Do I accept the reality
OL,7,Fthat homes will be built? I do accept
OL,8,Fit. We are a pragmatic group. What I
OL,9,Fwon't accept is that homes are built
OL,10,Fat any cost and that biodiversity is
OL,11,Fignored."
OL,13,FSteve Hawkins has been grazing council-
OL,14,Fowned land next to the meadows for 45
OL,15,Fyears. But he's now been told his
OL,16,Ftenancy will end in November.
OL,18,FThe 11.5 acres will instead be used as
OL,19,Fpart of biodiversity net gain for the
OL,20,Fdevelopment - to offset the
OL,21,Fbiodiversity lost as part of new laws.
OL,26,@nD@LOUsD@IO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1773392677
OL,3,CControversial plans to build homes on
OL,4,Chistoric grassland set to be approved
OL,6,FHe says he will likely be forced out
OL,7,Fof the city.
OL,9,FSteve said: "I'm devastated,
OL,10,Fcompletely devastated. For the last
OL,11,Ffew decades this has been my life. I
OL,12,Fkeep it tidy and look after it. But
OL,13,Fthat doesn't mean nothing. We're going
OL,14,Fto have to walk away.
OL,16,F"We'll have to start out life all over
OL,17,Fagain now. We don't know what we're
OL,18,Fgoing to do."
OL,26,@qD@MOUzD@MO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1773392677
OL,3,CControversial plans to build homes on
OL,4,Chistoric grassland set to be approved
OL,6,FCouncillor Stephen Williams, Chair of
OL,7,Fthe Public Health and Communities
OL,8,FCommittee, said: "The land around
OL,9,FVictory Park has been identified as a
OL,10,Fpotential site to be improved for
OL,11,Fnature.
OL,13,F"It is a requirement of the
OL,14,FBrislington Meadows housing
OL,15,Fdevelopment that natural habitats are
OL,16,Fcreated or enhanced so that the
OL,17,Fquality and variety of plant and
OL,18,Fanimal life present is better after
OL,19,Fthe development than it was before,
OL,20,Fcontributing to nature recovery.
OL,26,@pD@ROU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1773392677
OL,3,CControversial plans to build homes on
OL,4,Chistoric grassland set to be approved
OL,6,F"The grazing that currently takes
OL,7,Fplace on the land needs to come to an
OL,8,Fend to allow habitats to be changed or
OL,9,Fenhanced. The land will then be
OL,10,Fmanaged, for a minimum of 30 years, in
OL,11,Fa way that will benefit nature.
OL,13,F"To ensure the area is available to
OL,14,Fbegin the new land management approach
OL,15,Fthat will improve the site for nature,
OL,16,Fachieving a gain of at least 10% in
OL,17,Fbiodiversity, the tenants have been
OL,18,Fgiven notice to vacate the land.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
